title: Zalman CNPS 9X Optima CPU Cooler, Ultra Quiet Air Cooler with White LED 120mm Fan, Direct Touch Heat-Pipes, 180W TDP, Pure Copper and Aluminum - Fits Intel and AMD, CNPS9X Optima
features: EXCELLENT COOLING PERFORMANCE: pure aluminum radiation fin and 4 pure copper heat pipes provide rapid cooling performance, up to 180W TDP, 60.89 CFM, Max 26 dBA, 1500 RPM

WHITE LED 120MM FAN: Low noise 120mm PWM fan with rifle bearing ensures a long life and quiet operations, 4-Pin PWM control automatically adjusts RPM to the temperature of the CPU. Fans operates 600-1500 RPM with high max airflow of 60.89 CFM

DIRECT TOUCH TECHNOLOGY: The DTH Direct Touch Heatpipe technology, which transfers Heat from the CPU to heatpipes directly, is used for minimizing thermal resistance and maximizing cooling performance
LONG LIFE RIFLE BEARING: Fan has rifle bearings for low noise, durability, and smooth operations. Fan measures 120mm x 120mm x 25mm
Compatible with Intel LGA115X/LGA1200: AMD AM4/ AM3+/ AM3/ FM2+/ FM2 CPU & APUs
description: ZALMAN's CNPS9X cooling solution w/ Direct Touch Heat pipes, low noise 120mm PWM white LED fan w/long-life rifle bearing.
